iv class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"ansaa-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"ansaa-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"ansaa-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"arpg5-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"arpg5-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"arpg5-0-0\">Following the guidelines laid out by\u202f\u202fGovernor Beshear, the Cabinet for Health and Family Services, and the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, our team has been working diligently to create and modify plans as this situation unfolds, working to minimize the risk for our residents, clients, and team members.\u202f\u202f<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"19ip9-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"19ip9-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"19ip9-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"72q6i-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"72q6i-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"72q6i-0-0\">While our nation is facing uncertainty, those in our care still need us. Our residents are still here with team members committed to taking care of them 24 hours a day.\u202fTeam members who can work from home are connecting virtually instead of meeting face-to-face.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"1h5fv-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"1h5fv-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"1h5fv-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"34a54-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"34a54-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"34a54-0-0\">The team members of our Kosair Charities Pediatric Convalescent Center provide care for the most vulnerable children of our Commonwealth.\u202fThey are extremely susceptible to contagious viruses, and we have limited access to that area of the campus to anyone who isn\u2019t an essential provider of care. We have restricted access to our Residential Treatment and Emergency Shelter area and closed our Aquatic Therapy Center to the public.\u202fNon-emergency services provided at Open Arms Children\u2019s Health have been temporarily suspended.\u202fAll of this is an effort to minimize any spread of the virus among our residents and team members.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"5rbt4-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"5rbt4-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"5rbt4-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"6hq7j-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"6hq7j-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"6hq7j-0-0\">This outbreak has already and will continue to impact resources for our organization and all non-profit organizations. Our community\u2019s compassion and dedication to our purpose is more important now than ever, and we are deeply appreciative for all the support you provide.\u202f<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"eecd3-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"eecd3-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"eecd3-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"btvnp-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"btvnp-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"btvnp-0-0\">There are ways you can continue to support Home of the Innocents from a distance during these difficult times.\u202fMore information about our mission, how we are responding to this crisis and ways to still support us are available on\u202f<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span class=\"py34i1dx\"><span data-offset-key=\"btvnp-1-0\">www.homeoftheinnocents.org<\/span><\/span><\/a><span data-offset-key=\"btvnp-2-0\">.\u202fYou can also find our Amazon Wish List at\u202f<a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/hz\/wishlist\/ls\/2U0WOFJA72T1G\/ref=cm_go_nav_hz\">www.amazon.com\/hz\/wishlist\/ls\/2U0WOFJA72T1G\/ref=cm_go_nav_hz<\/a><\/span><span data-offset-key=\"btvnp-4-0\">, where you can see our most needed items, order, and have them shipped directly to us.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"e1934-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"e1934-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"e1934-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"cu6jo-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"cu6jo-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"cu6jo-0-0\">We greatly appreciate your support of our mission and those we serve, especially during difficult times like these.\u202fWithout you, we would not be able to enrich the lives of children and families with hope, health and happiness. Thank you for all you do for Home of the Innocents and for all you are doing to support our community during these challenging times. Our thoughts are with you and your family during this time of uncertainty. We will get through this together.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"1mkhc-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"1mkhc-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"1mkhc-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"28nas\" data-offset-key=\"95ubl-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"95ubl-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"95ubl-0-0\">Paul Robinson, President &amp; CEO and Remy Noble, Board of Directors Chairperson<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Dear Friends, \u00a0 Along with each of you, we continue to learn and adapt to the fast-pa